Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管回忆溢满心头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓在干掉的泪痕中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以迎接朋友的方式\N温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年才刚过完没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青少年们就开始失控浮躁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,客人,客人\N你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔,明天就是第一次共通考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#03 暗夜中心跳不已\N和响子单独相处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考生真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要对五代多关心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是最后的紧要关头\N他一定紧张得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次共通考试\N明天终于要登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,有自信我就不会烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这一年\N就应该更努力用功一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还没做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,连手都还没牵到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么\N当然是管理员的事罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在什么都还没做…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞争对手又少了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去跟四谷和朱美他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们不要吵五代念书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从朱美开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊?有什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事,请快点过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快点过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你是怎么了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这么少当然会冷罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样的话\N你铁定会重考第二次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶,重考第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你找我有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天五代要参加第一次共通考试\N我想告诉你不要刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要穿得这么清凉\N在公寓里走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我刚才想对你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!不准看!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你不在家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,四谷不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快趁现在来个总复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷出现了,四谷出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了,你怎么会知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候来的?\N从哪里进来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚刚一直就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我是怎么进来的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(秘密)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又挖了一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,你立刻离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你好冷漠喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,今天对五代而言\N是非常重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再对他恶作剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶好耶,终于进入状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛打我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼去外面玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,这个走廊最好滑了\N(“滑”音同“落榜”)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你居然说了我最忌讳的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被重考生打了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么一句话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有别的话说了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐吧,汁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人明天要考试\N脾气难免大了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生就可以为所欲为吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以打弱小的小孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等考完试再加倍奉还就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子,你一定要等我到考试通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个社会\N都对重考生那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊溜滑板有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑板不能滑的话\N还有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说说话啊,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能说“滑”这个字!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑!滑!我想要溜滑板!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要溜滑板,我想要溜滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之进屋里去就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的…雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会变成泪雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天没有念到的部分\N要一口气追回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我的房间当作宴会厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里早就变成宴会厅了\N有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干嘛?你来干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,你不是说考试要到了\N不可以吵重考生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦,他已经变成\N没听到宴会吵闹声就无法念书了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正明天他一定会很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要好好地疯一疯\N让他壮烈地成仁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你们又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我郑重地再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试的季节就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请暂时不要去吵五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五代面前绝对不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考\N之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连开玩笑都不能喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不能说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你大声一点再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我要去朋友家念书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能办得到!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你一定办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,这是什么烂环境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋…鞋带断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉祥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经超越了\N“不吉祥”这个字能形容的范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要气馁,明年还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种奇怪的话安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说\N四谷说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊\N明年考不上的话,还有后年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你们不要太过份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我真的要生气罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛气成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从白天就一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N管理员对重考生有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不出面的话\N你们一定会没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敷衍、欺骗、前后不一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员的脸变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为五代着想而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变主意不出门了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回报你的一片真心\N我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还真乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员对我有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们这一栋停电耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是保险丝烧断了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你要念书…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电怎么念书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪,保险丝没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是配线出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话,先看看配线图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会修吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会,且工具都很齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对维修也略懂一二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在这里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:16:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次来这个阁楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处在暗室里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这里是个钟塔小屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那个坏掉的时钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有种古老图书馆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像古董店的店头摆饰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻馆的历史真的很悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么时候建的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了,青春的一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭和15年(1940年)3月13日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待再相逢\N昭和19年(1944年)10月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在战争期间写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时代\N爱上一个人一定很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争不晓得拆散了多少对情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们活着的这个时代\N真是和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前住在这里的人\N已经变成回忆的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一刻馆的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我会喜欢上一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小樱\N昭和19年(1944年),一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一段没有结局的爱情吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心看出神了,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点把停电修好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我得努力把它修好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为明天是你的重要日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员\N什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为了我这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了你着想,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说你们一直没回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,来吧\N不用在意我们,请继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在胡说些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在对她养的狗道歉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才摔倒的时候\N好像有撞到头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一只老鼠烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是它咬断了电线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是时钟的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个时钟早就坏掉了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应坏了的钟塔时钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得为什么突然响了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的钟声,在下着雨的城镇中\N整夜响个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正整晚都没睡\N顺便出来送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会再开宴会安慰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他滑得还真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话已经持续说了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是迟迟没有上榜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N‘响子紧张万分?五代考试中’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?\N他居然从考场逃了出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要陪他去应考
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨个眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.95,0:24:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经可以相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.63,0:25:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.62,0:25:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨

